Diaspora Engagement & Involve diaspora in development & Pravasi Bharatiya Divas \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}

\section*{Conclusion}

India’s 2025 landscape drives youth migration, with Gen Z seeking opportunities abroad amidst domestic challenges. The diaspora’s contributions are crucial for India’s development goals. Social work must adapt to support migrants and engage the diaspora, fostering a more inclusive society.

